<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="break-away-from">break away (from)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>离开；脱离；突然挣脱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When Abraham Lincoln was elected President, the southern states broke away and formed a new nation. 
当亚伯拉罕·林肯当选为总统时，南部州脱离出去，成立了一个新的国家。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He decided to break away from home after graduation. 
毕业后，他决定离开家。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He grabbed her, but she managed to break away from him.
他抓住了她，可她设法挣脱了。</p></div></div>